l_zhb_niz = l_zhb_niz_1m peres_niz_x = peres_niz_1_1m peres_niz_2 = peres_niz_2_1m peres_verh_x = peres_verh_1m l_zhb_verh = l_zhb_verh_1m
gosub "zhb" SECT_ATTRS sht_zhb, 19, 1, pen_zhb, ltype material mat_l_niz PRISM_ NSP/3, -b_l, get(NSP) if t_pol_l > 0 and show_pokr then gosub "pokr" SECT_ATTRS sht_stup, 19, 1, pen_stup material mat_stup PRISM_ NSP/3, -b_l, get(NSP) endif ENDGROUP
GROUP "second_m" if issecondm then del top rotx 90 addz -(b_l + b_zazor) addy h_plosh addx (int(h_plosh/h_stup)-1)*l_stup mulx -1
n_stup = ns_2m l_l_t = l_2m h_l_t = h_2m dl_zhb_verh_t = dl_zhb_verh dl_zhb_niz_t = peres_verh_1m - l_1m + l_stup isendstuppokr_t = isendstuppokr itype_pr_niz_t = 3 itype_pr_verh_t = itype_pr_verh
l_zhb_niz = l_zhb_niz_2m peres_niz_x = peres_niz_1_2m peres_niz_2 = peres_niz_2_2m peres_verh_x = peres_verh_2m l_zhb_verh = l_zhb_verh_2m
gosub "zhb" SECT_ATTRS sht_zhb, 19, 1, pen_zhb, ltype material mat_l_niz PRISM_ NSP/3, -b_l, get(NSP) if t_pol_l > 0 and show_pokr then gosub "pokr" SECT_ATTRS sht_stup, 19, 1, pen_stup material mat_stup PRISM_ NSP/3, -b_l, get(NSP) endif endif ENDGROUP
GROUP "plosh" if issecondm then del top mulx -1 rotz 180 addz h_plosh - t_pol_plosh addx l_zhb_verh_1m addy - 2 * b_l - b_zazor gosub "plosh"
SECT_ATTRS sht_zhb, 19, 1, pen_zhb, ltype material mat_l_niz
if t_pol_plosh > 0 and show_pokr then PRISM_ NSP/3, -t_plosh, use(NSP) material mat_stup SECT_ATTRS sht_stup, 19, 1, pen_stup PRISM_ NSP/3, t_pol_plosh, get(NSP) else PRISM_ NSP/3, -t_plosh, get(NSP) endif endif ENDGROUP
GROUP "plosh_2" if isplosh then del top if issecondm then rotz 180 addz h_l - t_pol_plosh addx -l_1m+l_2m addy - 2 * b_l - b_zazor HOTSPOT 0, b_2_plosh, 0, unID, l_2_plosh, 1+128: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT l_2_plosh, b_2_plosh, 0, unID, l_2_plosh, 2: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT l_2_plosh, 0, 0, unID, b_2_plosh, 1+128: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT l_2_plosh, b_2_plosh, 0, unID, b_2_plosh, 2: unID=unID+1 else addx l_1m - l_stup addz h_l - t_pol_plosh HOTSPOT 0, b_2_plosh, 0, unID, l_2_plosh, 1+128: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT l_2_plosh, b_2_plosh, 0, unID, l_2_plosh, 2: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT l_2_plosh, 0, 0, unID, b_2_plosh, 1+128: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT l_2_plosh, b_2_plosh, 0, unID, b_2_plosh, 2: unID=unID+1 l_zhb_verh_2m = l_zhb_verh_1m l_2m = l_1m endif gosub "plosh_2" SECT_ATTRS sht_zhb, 19, 1, pen_zhb, ltype material mat_l_niz if t_pol_plosh > 0 and show_pokr then PRISM_ NSP/3, -t_plosh, use(NSP) material mat_stup SECT_ATTRS sht_stup, 19, 1, pen_stup PRISM_ NSP/3, t_pol_plosh, get(NSP) else PRISM_ NSP/3, -t_plosh, get(NSP) endif endif ENDGROUP
if itype_pr_niz = 2 then startx = peres_niz_1_1m else startx = peres_niz_2_1m endif starty = 0.5 * b_l HOTSPOT startx, starty,0, unID, dl_zhb_niz, 1+128: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT startx+1, starty,0, unID, dl_zhb_niz, 3: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT startx-dl_zhb_niz, starty,0, unID, dl_zhb_niz, 2: unID=unID+1
if issecondm then del top startx = (h_plosh/h_stup)*l_stup - ((h_l-h_plosh)/h_stup)*l_stup starty = 1.5 * b_l + b_zazor HOTSPOT startx, starty,0, unID, h_l, 1+128: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT startx, starty,h_l, unID, h_l, 2: unID=unID+1
startx = l_1m - l_2m - l_stup starty = 1.5 * b_l + b_zazor HOTSPOT startx, starty,h_l - t_pol_plosh, unID, dl_zhb_verh, 1+128: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT startx+1, starty,h_l - t_pol_plosh, unID, dl_zhb_verh, 3: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT startx-dl_zhb_verh, starty,h_l - t_pol_plosh, unID, dl_zhb_verh, 2: unID=unID+1
startx = (int(h_plosh/h_stup)-1)*l_stup starty = b_l + b_zazor/2 HOTSPOT startx, starty,0, unID, h_plosh, 1+128: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT startx, starty,h_plosh, unID, h_plosh, 2: unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT startx, starty,h_plosh, unID, l_plosh, 1+128: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT startx+l_plosh, starty,h_plosh, unID, l_plosh, 2: unID=unID+1 PLACEGROUP "first_m" PLACEGROUP "second_m" PLACEGROUP "plosh" else del top startx = (h_l/h_stup)*l_stup starty = 0.5 * b_l HOTSPOT startx, starty, 0, unID, h_l, 1+128: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT startx, starty, h_l, unID, h_l, 2: unID=unID+1
startx = peres_verh_1m starty = 0.5 * b_l HOTSPOT startx, starty,h_l - t_pol_plosh, unID, dl_zhb_verh, 1+128: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT startx-1, starty,h_l - t_pol_plosh, unID, dl_zhb_verh, 3: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT startx+dl_zhb_verh, starty,h_l - t_pol_plosh, unID, dl_zhb_verh, 2: unID=unID+1
PLACEGROUP "first_m" endif
del top if isplosh then PLACEGROUP "plosh_2"
end
"plosh": !====================================================================================================================================================================== !============= Площадка ==================== put 0, 0, scode put 0, b_l, scode put l_zhb_niz+t_pol_l, b_l, scode put l_zhb_niz+t_pol_l, b_l + b_zazor, scode put 0, b_l + b_zazor, scode put 0, 2* b_l + b_zazor, scode put l_plosh + l_zhb_niz, 2* b_l + b_zazor, scode put l_plosh + l_zhb_niz, 0, scode !====================================================================================================================================================================== return
"plosh_2": !====================================================================================================================================================================== !============= Площадка ==================== put (l_zhb_verh_2m-l_2m+l_stup), 0, scode if b_2_plosh > b_l then put (l_zhb_verh_2m-l_2m+l_stup), b_l, scode put t_pol_l, b_l, scode put t_pol_l, b_2_plosh, scode else put (l_zhb_verh_2m-l_2m+l_stup), b_2_plosh, scode endif put l_2_plosh, b_2_plosh, scode put l_2_plosh, 0, scode !====================================================================================================================================================================== return
"zhb": !====================================================================================================================================================================== !============= Ж/б ==================== !--------- Первая ступень -------------- !Опирание на плиту if itype_pr_niz_t = 1 then put t_pol_l, -t_pol_niz, scode peres_niz_y = -t_pol_niz else !Сбоку к плите if itype_pr_niz_t = 2 then t_pol_niz_t = t_pol_niz t_pl_niz_t = t_pl_niz else t_pol_niz_t = t_pol_plosh t_pl_niz_t = t_plosh endif peres_niz_y = - t_pol_niz_t - t_pl_niz_t put peres_niz_x, peres_niz_y, scode put peres_niz_x, -t_pol_niz_t-t_pl_niz_t, scode put l_zhb_niz, -t_pol_niz_t-t_pl_niz_t, scode put l_zhb_niz, -t_pol_niz_t, scode put peres_niz_2, -t_pol_niz_t, scode put t_pol_l, -t_pol_l, scode endif !--------- Промежуточные ступени -------------- for i = 1 to n_stup-1 x = l_stup * i+t_pol_l y = h_stup * i-t_pol_l put x-l_stup, y, scode put x, y, scode next i !--------- Последняя ступень -------------- !Сбоку к плите if itype_pr_verh_t = 2 then t_pol_verh_t = t_pol_verh t_pl_verh_t = t_pl_verh else t_pol_verh_t = t_pol_plosh t_pl_verh_t = t_plosh endif if isendstuppokr_t then t_pol_l_t = t_pol_verh_t else t_pol_l_t = t_pol_l endif put l_stup*(n_stup-1)+t_pol_l, h_stup*n_stup-t_pol_l_t, scode if not(isendstuppokr_t) then put l_l_t, h_l_t - t_pol_l_t, scode put l_l_t, h_l_t - t_pol_verh_t, scode endif put l_zhb_verh, h_l_t - t_pol_verh_t, scode put l_zhb_verh, h_l_t - t_pol_verh_t - t_pl_verh_t, scode put peres_verh_x, h_l_t - t_pol_verh_t - t_pl_verh_t, scode put peres_niz_x, peres_niz_y, scode for i = 0 to 1 th = -i * b_l hotspot t_pol_l,-t_pol_l,th hotspot peres_niz_2,-t_pol_niz_t,th hotspot peres_niz_x,-t_pl_niz_t-t_pol_niz_t,th hotspot l_zhb_niz,-t_pl_niz_t-t_pol_niz_t,th hotspot l_zhb_niz,-t_pol_niz_t,th hotspot l_l_t,h_l_t-t_pol_verh_t,th hotspot l_l_t,h_l_t-t_pol_verh_t,th hotspot peres_verh_x,h_l_t - t_pol_verh_t - t_pl_verh_t,th hotspot l_zhb_verh,h_l_t - t_pol_verh_t - t_pl_verh_t,th hotspot l_zhb_verh,h_l_t-t_pol_verh_t,th next i !====================================================================================================================================================================== return
"pokr": !====================================================================================================================================================================== !============= Покрытие ==================== !--------- Первая ступень !Опирание на плиту if itype_pr_niz_t = 1 then put t_pol_l, -t_pol_niz, scode put 0, -t_pol_niz, scode put 0, 0, scode endif
!Сбоку к плите if itype_pr_niz_t = 2 or itype_pr_niz_t = 3 then put t_pol_l, -t_pol_l, scode put peres_niz_2, -t_pol_niz_t, scode put l_zhb_niz, -t_pol_niz_t, scode put l_zhb_niz, 0, scode endif
put 0, 0, scode !--------- Верх покрытия --------- for i = 1 to n_stup-1 y = h_stup * i x = l_stup * i put x-l_stup, y, scode put x, y, scode next i put l_l_t-l_stup, h_stup*n_stup, scode if isendstuppokr_t then t_pol_l_t = t_pol_verh_t else t_pol_l_t = t_pol_l endif !--------- Поворачиваем вниз и вбок --------- put l_zhb_verh, h_stup*n_stup, scode put l_zhb_verh, h_stup*n_stup-t_pol_verh_t, scode put l_l_t, h_stup*n_stup-t_pol_verh_t, scode put l_l_t, h_stup*n_stup-t_pol_l_t, scode put l_stup*(n_stup-1)+t_pol_l, h_stup*n_stup-t_pol_l_t, scode
!--------- Низ покрытия --------- for i = n_stup-1 to 1 step -1 x = l_stup*(i)+t_pol_l y = h_stup*(i)-t_pol_l put x, y, scode put x-l_stup, y, scode next i !--------- Поворачиваем вниз и вбок --------- put t_pol_l, h_stup-t_pol_l, scode put t_pol_l, 0, scode !====================================================================================================================================================================== return

endif
return
"simb_niz_1": line2 startx,0,endx,0 line2 startx,b_l,endx,b_l line2 endx,0,endx,b_l
if show_ogr and show_pokr then LINE_TYPE line_ogr x1 = 0 : y1 = b_l-ogr_left : x2 = l_l_t : y2 = b_l-ogr_left : gosub "hline" x1 = 0 : y1 = ogr_right : x2 = l_l_t : y2 = ogr_right : gosub "hline" LINE_TYPE line_2d endif xv = endx : xn = startx gosub "strel" line2 xn,b_l/2,xv,b_l/2 line2 startx,b_l/2,endx,b_l/2 for xs = startx to endx step l_stup x1 = xs : y1 = 0 : x2 = xs : y2 = b_l : gosub "hline" next xs return
"simb_niz_2": HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, cut_x_niz_1, 1+128: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 cut_x_niz_1, 0, unID, cut_x_niz_1, 2: unID=unID+1 line2 0,0,cut_x_niz_1,0 line2 0,b_l,cut_x_niz_1+dx_cut,b_l line2 cut_x_niz_1,0,cut_x_niz_1+dx_cut,b_l
if show_ogr and show_pokr then LINE_TYPE line_ogr x1 = 0 : y1 = b_l-ogr_left : x2 = cut_x_niz_1+dx_cut : y2 = b_l-ogr_left : gosub "hline" x1 = 0 : y1 = ogr_right : x2 = cut_x_niz_1 : y2 = ogr_right : gosub "hline" LINE_TYPE line_2d endif
x1 = cut_x_niz_1 : x2 = cut_x_niz_1 + dx_cut : y1 = 0 : y2 = b_l !Линия разрыва x3 = 0 : x4 = l_l_t : y3 = b_l/2 : y4 = y3 !Центральная линия gosub "getXY1" : xv = x : xn = 0 line2 xn,b_l/2,xv,b_l/2 gosub "strel" for xs = 0 to l_l_t step l_stup if xs <= cut_x_niz_1 then x1 = xs : y1 = 0 : x2 = xs : y2 = b_l : gosub "hline" endif if (xs > cut_x_niz_1) and (xs <= cut_x_niz_1+dx_cut) then x1 = xs : x2 = xs : y1 = b_l : y2 = 0 !Линия ступени x3 = cut_x_niz_1 + dx_cut : x4 = cut_x_niz_1 : y3 = b_l : y4 = 0 !Линия разрыва gosub "getXY1" x1 = xs : y1 = y : x2 = xs : y2 = b_l : gosub "hline" endif next xs return
"simb_niz_3": HOTSPOT2 l_l_t, 0, unID, cut_x_niz_2, 1+128: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 l_l_t - cut_x_niz_2, 0, unID, cut_x_niz_2, 2: unID=unID+1 line2 l_l_t,0,l_l_t - cut_x_niz_2,0 line2 l_l_t,b_l,l_l_t - cut_x_niz_2+dx_cut,b_l line2 l_l_t-cut_x_niz_2,0,l_l_t-cut_x_niz_2+dx_cut,b_l
if show_ogr and show_pokr then LINE_TYPE line_ogr x1 = l_l_t : y1 = b_l-ogr_left : x2 = l_l_t - cut_x_niz_2+dx_cut : y2 = b_l-ogr_left : gosub "hline" x1 = l_l_t : y1 = ogr_right : x2 = l_l_t - cut_x_niz_2 : y2 = ogr_right : gosub "hline" LINE_TYPE line_2d endif
x1 = l_l_t-cut_x_niz_2 : x2 = l_l_t-cut_x_niz_2 + dx_cut : y1 = 0 : y2 = b_l !Линия разрыва x3 = 0 : x4 = l_l_t : y3 = b_l/2 : y4 = y3 !Центральная линия gosub "getXY1" : xv = l_l_t : xn = x gosub "strel" line2 xn, b_l/2, xv, b_l/2 for xs = 0 to l_l_t step l_stup if xs > l_l_t - cut_x_niz_2 + dx_cut then x1 = xs : y1 = 0 : x2 = xs : y2 = b_l : gosub "hline" endif if (xs > l_l_t-cut_x_niz_2) and (xs <= l_l_t-cut_x_niz_2+dx_cut) then x1 = xs : x2 = xs : y1 = b_l : y2 = 0 !Линия ступени x3 = l_l_t-cut_x_niz_2 + dx_cut : x4 = l_l_t-cut_x_niz_2 : y3 = b_l : y4 = 0 !Линия разрыва gosub "getXY1" x1 = xs : y1 = y : x2 = xs : y2 = 0 : gosub "hline" endif next xs return
"simb_niz_4": HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, cut_x_niz_1, 1+128: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 cut_x_niz_1, 0, unID, cut_x_niz_1, 2: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 l_l_t, 0, unID, cut_x_niz_2, 1+128: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 l_l_t - cut_x_niz_2, 0, unID, cut_x_niz_2, 2: unID=unID+1
line2 cut_x_niz_1,0,l_l_t - cut_x_niz_2,0 line2 cut_x_niz_1 + dx_cut,b_l,l_l_t - cut_x_niz_2 + dx_cut,b_l
if show_ogr and show_pokr then LINE_TYPE line_ogr x1 = cut_x_niz_1 : y1 = ogr_right : x2 = l_l_t - cut_x_niz_2 : y2 = ogr_right : gosub "hline" x1 = cut_x_niz_1 + dx_cut : y1 = b_l-ogr_left : x2 = l_l_t - cut_x_niz_2 + dx_cut : y2 = b_l-ogr_left : gosub "hline" LINE_TYPE line_2d endif
line2 l_l_t-cut_x_niz_2,0,l_l_t-cut_x_niz_2+dx_cut,b_l line2 cut_x_niz_1,0,cut_x_niz_1+dx_cut,b_l
